            "answer": "<p>Fat tire electric trikes for adults are worth choosing mainly for fat tires provide excellent stability, superior shock absorption, and reliable traction on almost any surface. From city streets to gravel roads, they help you ride more confidently over rough terrain, loose ground, or wet conditions.</p>"
