            "answer": "<p>Yes, e-trikes are remarkably safe overall. For most people, especially seniors or those with poor balance, it is safer than a traditional two wheel drive electric bike. Its main advantage is its stability, so you do not need to worry about losing balance or falling when stopping or getting on and off.</p>"
          }
        },
