            "answer": "<p>A best electric tricycle for adults should include these key features: a UL-certified Samsung-cell battery pack,750W rear-drive motor, rear differential, safety lights, disc brakes, parking brake, and a step-thru frame. These features work together to improve stability and reduce the risk of tipping, ensuring a smooth, safe, and comfortable ride. The Maxfoot MF30 and MF33 offer all of these essential features.</p>"
          }
        },
